title: Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate, 2/16/2011 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
February 16, 2011

 



Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate, 2/16/2011





NOMINATIONS SENT TO THE SENATE:

	Timothy M. Cain, of South Carolina, to be United States District Judge for the District of South Carolina, vice P. Michael Duffy, retired.

	Scott Wesley Skavdahl, of Wyoming, to be United States District Judge for the District of Wyoming, vice William F. Downes, retiring.
